sub_title: Computer Science & Engineering Student TU Delft | Heineken Data Analyst Intern | Faculty Student Council EEMCS
summary: Obtaining my bachelor degree in Computer Science & Engineering is currently my primary objective next to building managerial skills and knowledge on internal affairs and sustainable development through engagements in Formula Student Team Delft, Model United Nations and other extra-curricular activities. Over the past years I also had the opportunity to go beyond academic activities through short assignments in globally operating companies based in both Singapore and the Netherlands.
